Log-Lager Changes:

Restructured header to use a separate array reference.
Added support for extraction of named type information in header.

Added TypedMessage support.
Changes to headers to meet evolving work standards.

0.02:  2011-05-09
Initial "de-workified" release.

0.04.07: 2011-11-03
"file" output now supports common log-rolling behaviors.

0.99: Upcoming
Completely revamped and refactored.
 * New public API
 * Pluggable modules for
   - Output (e.g. STDERR, Syslog, File)
   - Configuration management 
   - Message format
 * More tests
 * New docs

